#originalStanceText=No
#originalTopic=Debate:_Same_sex_marriage_ban
 Gay marriage would be no worse for the "institution of marriage" than a number of other existing harmful legal unions Many menaces to society are allowed to marry. They often become terrible, neglectful parents. Yet, this does not provide cause to deprive these individuals of the right to marry. Even if homosexuals were somehow concluded to be sub-optimal parents, this is not a valid rationale for denying them the right to merry.
